pageProduct.name: Swisse Kids Bone Health 60 Gummies
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Kids Bone Health Gummies are a premium quality formula to help develop and maintain healthy and strong bones and teeth in children. Made with natural colours and flavours, these great-tasting gummies are 99.9% sugar free and are ideal for fussy eaters and growing children on the go.

Swisse Kids Bone Health Gummies are a premium quality formula to help develop and maintain healthy and strong bones and teeth in children:
- Calcium assists the development and maintenance of healthy, strong bones and maintains teeth health
- Vitamin D3 assists with calcium absorption, supports bone health and helps support the immune system

Benefits:
- Great tasting for fussy eaters
- Natural Strawberry & Vanilla Flavour
- 99.9% Sugar Free
- No artificial sweeteners
- Naturally sweetened with Stevia
- No added dairy or lactose

Size: 60 Gummies

Warnings

Vitamin & mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet. This medicine contains maltitol & mannitol (Total 5g per maximum daily dose) and may have a laxative effect or cause diarrheoa. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional

Ingredients

CALCIUM (from calcium phosphate) 100mg
VITAMIN D3 (colecalciferol) 5mcg
Contains Sulfites.

No added lactose, yeast, egg, soy, artificial colours or flavours

Directions

2-8 years: Chew 2 gummy daily, during or immediately after a meal.
9-12 years: Chew 3 gummies daily, during or immediately after a meal.
Or as directed by a healthcare professional. Do not swallow whole.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
